ght up in the pursuit of holiness, and provide a key to understanding the resilience of Catholic culture in an age of religious change and conflict.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 4aGender Studies. 4aHistory.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertCornell University Press Backlist 2000-2013z978311053615740uhttps://doi.org/10.7591/978150172100740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781501721007423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781501721007/original  a978-3-11-053615-7  Cornell University Press Backlist 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles